Name: Linus
Owner: @lineysofiney 
Summary: Linus has a super power. Whenever he doesn’t get what he wants he can puke on demand. This ain’t a normal puke. It’s more of a projectile vomit. We know there’s a super hero or villain or something that we can make a joke about. But honestly, the name ain’t coming to us. So yeah, thats it for now.
•
Has been on a diet for 2 months so far and will get her first weigh in next month!

node.text:
•
Name: Chimi
Owner: @chimichanga_cat
Summary: A LIL CHIMI CHONGGGG. Gotta love a fellow Canuck. Chimi is very proud of her heritage and has lived in Canada all her life. Yes the rumours are true, she does ride her polar bear to school everyday and also eats nothing but maple syrup. Doesn’t that sound like the dream? Everyone should move to Canada.
•
Has been on a diet for 2 months so far and will get her first weigh in next month!

Name: Tubbs
Owner: @ed_mather 
Summary: Being short and stocky is making Tubbs a terrific fighter. Every night he goes out in the streets searching for the goods. What are the goods? We don’t know. But Tubbs has already beat up 207 Chonks this year just to get the goods. 
•
Tubbs is trying his hardest to start losing weight on his diet!
